function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	tCannibals = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Step_Guulrahn_02_CannibalVignette")

	--cry for help
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Actor_Victim) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(Actor_Victim) then
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(Actor_Victim, Hydra.TEAM_PLAYER_DEFAULT)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_VILLAGER, Actor_Victim)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Actor_Victim, VIllager_MoveTo_Loc, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(Actor_Victim, animset_cower)
	end
	
	--Move victim then enable cannibal and attack victim
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	for id, idCannibal in pairs(tCannibals) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCannibal) then
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idCannibal, true)
			Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idCannibal, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
		end
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(Actor_Cannibal) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(Actor_Victim) then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTargetsFeet(Actor_Cannibal, Actor_Victim, "cannibal_twohand_leap")
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)
	--set cannibal to hostile
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Actor_Cannibal) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(Actor_Cannibal) then
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(Actor_Cannibal, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_0)
	end

end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Actor_Victim) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(Actor_Victim) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(Actor_Victim)
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(Actor_Victim, idActorKiller)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_Villager_Survived, Actor_Victim)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Actor_Victim) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(Actor_Victim) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Actor_Victim, Villager_MoveTo_End, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(Actor_Victim, 1.0)
	end
end
